data.description: Welcome to this newly completely remodeled two story brick home on Evansville’s Northside. Located in Shady Hills subdivision, you will want to make this spacious gorgeous home your own. This home has plenty of space with 4 bedrooms including a roomy Master Suite with stunning all tiled walk-in shower as well as access to the upper balcony with lovely french doors. The upper floor boasts an immense family room with a large patio outside perfect for outdoor entertainment. The main bathroom has double vanities and a vintage cast iron tub as well as built-in storage. The main floor has a spacious living room with a cozy dining room complete with wainscoting just off the kitchen. The kitchen has loads of cabinets with a huge floor to ceiling pantry and all new stainless steel GE appliances. The ample 2.5 car garage has plenty of space for cars and a work area. New furnace and AC finish off this magnificent home.
